= The <span style="color: #6A1E1E;">**DSU**</span> Enters Government

With the favorable Bracht being installed at the head of the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span>, the party no longer voice loud reservations over the inclusion of the "reasonable" <span style="color: #6A1E1E;">**DSU**</span> into the Schleicher cabinet, to increase its popular backing, and to tame the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazis</span> that can be tamed. 

This goes completely against Schleicher's promise to us, that he'll never let the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazis</span> into cabinet if we were to give him a major concession. e have been conned, big time.

- @dsu_in_gov

